Hello! Thank you for calling NoteWorthy Music School. My name is Ralph Butler. How may I assist you today?

Hi, Ralph. I'm feeling a bit nervous about a billing issue. My name is Katherine Hughes.

Nice to meet you, Katherine. Don't worry, I'm here to help. Can you tell me what concerns you have about your billing?

I'm worried because I received an unexpected charge on my account.

I understand that can be concerning. Let me look into this for you. Could you please provide me with your billing account number?

Sure, my billing account number is two three four five six.

Thank you, Katherine. I will check the details. I also need to verify your registered email address for security purposes. Could you provide that as well?

Certainly, it's katherine dot hughes at example dot com.

Great, I appreciate that. I see the issue now, and it seems to be a duplicate charge which we can rectify. I will initiate a refund, and you should see it in your account within five business days.

Thank you so much, Ralph. That makes me feel a lot better.

You're welcome, Katherine. Thank you for reaching out to us. If you have any other questions, feel free to call. Have a wonderful day!
